INSERT INTO
  categories.categories_cars
  (park_id, car_id, category, updated_at, deleted, jdoc)
SELECT
  unnest($1) AS park_id,
  unnest($2) AS car_id,
  unnest($3) AS category,
  NOW() AS updated_at,
  FALSE AS deleted,
  unnest($4)::jsonb AS jdoc
ON CONFLICT
  (park_id, car_id, category)
DO UPDATE
SET
  updated_at = NOW(),
  deleted = FALSE,
  jdoc = EXCLUDED.jdoc
;

UPDATE
  categories.categories_cars AS dst
SET
  deleted = TRUE,
  updated_at = NOW()
FROM (
  SELECT DISTINCT
    unnest($1) AS park_id,
    unnest($2) AS car_id
) AS src
WHERE src.park_id = dst.park_id
  AND src.car_id = dst.car_id
;
begin isolation level read committed, read write
